INSTRUCTION 
-----------------------------
1. enter the folder named "server".
2. run the command -> nodemon server.js 
3. open browser with address localhost:5000



*tested on windows 10 for local implementation

INSTRUCTION 
-----------------------------
Client:
1. enter the folder named "client".
2. run the command -> npm install
3. run the command -> npm start

Server:
1. enter the folder named "server".
2. run the command -> npm install
3. run the command -> nodemon server.js 

